<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7775> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7775" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Aedile or Iudex quaestionis 86. See MRR 2.54, 57, note 3. The entries ought to be Aedile, 86, Iudex quaestionis, 85 (Sumner, Orators 111). Cf. Syme, CPh 50, 1955, 133.[17]\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4064> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4064" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Presided over the suit to recover the booty from Asculum from the estate of Pompeius Strabo, and betrothed his daughter to the young Pompey (Plut. Pomp. 4.1-3; cf. Cic. Brut. 230; Val. Max. 5.3.5). See Seidel, FA 49." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4063> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4063" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "3 Klebs (RE) plausibly identifies Antistius with the Tribune of 88 who died an aedilicius in 82. See Vell. 2.26.2; App. BC 1.88; Plut. Pomp. 9.2-3; Oros. 5.20-4, on his death." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4062> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4062" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Presided over the suit to recover the booty from Asculum from the estate of Pompeius Strabo, and betrothed his daughter to the young Pompey (Plut. Pomp. 4.1-3; cf. Cic. Brut. 230; Val. Max. 5.3.5). See Seidel, FA 49." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4061> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4061" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "3 Klebs (RE) plausibly identifies Antistius with the Tribune of 88 who died an aedilicius in 82. See Vell. 2.26.2; App. BC 1.88; Plut. Pomp. 9.2-3; Oros. 5.20-4, on his death." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3973> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3973" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Along with Sulpicius, he opposed the attempt of Julius Caesar Strabo to proceed to the consulship without first being Praetor (Cic. Brut. 226-227)." .
